(x-1)^n
-(x-1)^n
(1+x)^n=1+nx+ \frac{n(n-1)}{1 \cdot 2} x^2 + \frac{n(n-1)(n-2)}{1\cdot2\cdot3} x^3+\cdots
(-1)^n \bigg[\frac{n(n-1)}{1 \cdot 2}x^2 + \frac{n(n-1)(n-2)}{1\cdot2\cdot3} x^3+ \cdots \bigg]
(-1)^{n+1}\bigg[1+nx+ \frac{n(n-1)}{1 \cdot 2}x^2 + \frac{n(n-1)(n-2)}{1\cdot2\cdot3} x^3+ \cdots\bigg]
